text: Kylie and Garibay (stylized as Kylie + Garibay) are a musical duo. The members are Australian singer-songwriter Kylie Minogue and American record producer Fernando Garibay. They released their first extended play (EP), titled Sleepwalker, on September 24, 2014. ==References== Category:2014 establishments in California Category:Electronic music groups Category:Musical duos Category:Musical groups established in 2014
